text: Edona Kryeziu (born 3 October 1995) is a Kosovar footballer who plays as a forward and has appeared for the Kosovo women's national team. ==Career== Kryeziu has been capped for the Kosovo national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Kosovan women's footballers Category:Kosovo women's international footballers Category:Women's association football forwards Category:KFF Mitrovica players
